 Gibson 宣布 Jeff Beck 'YardBurst' 1959 Les Paul Standard 定制吉他https://www.nme.com/news/music/gibson-announce-jeff-beck-yardburst-1959-les-paul-standard-custom-guitar-3768477?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=gibson-announce-jeff- Beck-yardburst-1959-les-paul-标准-定制-吉他Liberty DunworthTue, 25 Jun 2024 11:51:04 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3768477 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Jeff Beck 与他的 1959 年《Dark Cherry Sunburst》中的 Les Paul Standard 以及 Gibson 的 2024 年复刻版" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这把吉他在他 80 岁生日那天到货，只生产了 130 个型号</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gibson-announce-jeff-beck-yardburst-1959-les-paul-standard-custom-guitar-3768477">Gibson 宣布 Jeff Beck &#39;YardBurst&#39; 1959 Les Paul Standard 定制吉他</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Jeff Beck 与他的 1959 年《Dark Cherry Sunburst》中的 Les Paul Standard 以及 Gibson 的 2024 年复刻版" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Gibson 分享了一款全新“YardBurst”1959 Les Paul Custom 的细节，这款吉他是为了纪念吉他偶像<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jeff-beck">杰夫·贝克 (Jeff Beck)</a>而制作的。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/music-greats-deaths-in-2023-3558913">缅怀 2023 年我们失去的音乐伟人</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>新型号的问世恰逢吉他制造商庆祝音乐历史 130 周年之际，也是这位传奇演奏家庆祝其 80 岁生日的同一天。</p><p>它向贝克首次出现在地图上时所使用的斧头致敬——他在作为 Yardbirds 的一员而声名鹊起时所使用的标志性 1959 年 Les Paul Standard。 “YardBurst”现已上市，是对历史吉他的忠实再现，其设计捕捉了其所有独特特征，包括经典的白色线轴双线圈和黑色单层护板。</p><p>为了纪念 Gibson 130 周年，仅制作了 130 把，每把都是在 Murphy Lab 手工制作的，并经过巧妙的老化，以匹配吉他手 Yardbird 时代原始型号的外观。</p><p>在此之前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/legendary-guitarist-jeff-beck-has-died-aged-78-3379009">，这位吉他先驱于去年 1 月意外去世</a>，享年 78 岁。 </p><figure id="attachment_3768480" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3768480" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3768480" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson-Body@2000x1270.jpg" alt="杰夫·贝克·吉布森《YardBurst》" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson-Body@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson-Body@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson-Body@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson-Body@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson-Body@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-Gibson-Body@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3768480" class="wp-caption-text">杰夫·贝克·吉布森《YardBurst》。图片来源：吉布森</figcaption></figure><p>“杰夫非常自豪拥有这把吉他的原版，”他的遗孀桑德拉·贝克 (Sandra Beck) 在谈到这款新产品时说道。 “他意识到并完全支持 Gibson Custom 为创造这把乐器所做的出色工作和热爱，并希望这把吉他能给演奏它的人带来数小时的快乐。”</p><p> Gibson 首席执行官 Cesar Gueikian 在宣布该型号时也表达了对 Beck 的敬意。 “杰夫是一位开拓者，我们吉他英雄中的吉他英雄，受到同时代人的钦佩，”他说。</p><p> “杰夫在 Yardbirds 时代的职业生涯早期对吉布森莱斯保罗的文化意义发挥了重要作用。就像 Jeff 受到 Les Paul 的影响一样，他也影响了许多标志性音乐家，让他们用 Gibson Les Paul 来创作艺术。我们很荣幸向杰夫致敬。”</p><p>贝克于 1965 年加入 The Yardbirds，接替<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eric-clapton">埃里克·克莱普顿 (Eric Clapton)</a> 。他与乐队合作了 12 个多月，并作为阵容的一部分与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jimmy-page">吉米·佩奇 (Jimmy Page)</a>进行了短暂合作。</p><p>该吉他采用深樱桃色 Sunburst 配色，并配有做旧的 Lifton 硬壳琴盒。它现在在 Gibson 上售价 8,999 英镑，但似乎已经售空。 <a href="https://www.gibson.com/en-GB/p/Electric-Guitar/Jeff-Beck-YardBurst-1959-Les-Paul-Standard/Dark-Cherry-Sunburst" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处</a>了解更多信息。 </p><figure id="attachment_3768479" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3768479" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3768479" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-certificate@2000x1270.jpg" alt="杰夫·贝克·吉布森“YardBurst”证书" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-certificate@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-certificate@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-certificate@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-certificate@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-certificate@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Jeff-Beck-certificate@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3768479" class="wp-caption-text">杰夫·贝克·吉布森“YardBurst”证书。图片来源：吉布森</figcaption></figure><p>在杰夫·贝克的其他新闻中，今年早些时候，已证实这位演奏家录制的最后一张录音室录音<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-mark-knopfler-star-studded-going-home-teenage-cancer-trust-3601691">出现在马克·诺普弗勒重新录制的版本“回家”中。</a></p><p>为了为青少年癌症信托基金会慈善机构筹集资金，这首歌曲被重新创作，并邀请了吉他界的一些大牌明星，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queen">Queen</a>乐队的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brian-may">Brian May</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">Bruce Springsteen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">Black Sabbath</a>的 Tony Iommi、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eric-clapton">Eric Clapton</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">Rolling。滚石</a>乐队吉他手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ronnie-wood">罗尼·伍德 (Ronnie Wood)</a>等。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gibson-announce-jeff-beck-yardburst-1959-les-paul-standard-custom-guitar-3768477">Gibson 宣布 Jeff Beck &#39;YardBurst&#39; 1959 Les Paul Standard 定制吉他</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
